This Load Confirmation is pursuant to our verbal agreement on 04/06/2022 1451 between RJW LOGISTICS (Broker) and
(Carrier). Both parties agree to the order details contained in this confirmation, including
pickup, delivery locations, any special instructions and the agreed rate listed below.
Compensation for this load will be forfeited and agreed will not be paid to the carrier contracted to this load if the carrier double-brokers
this shipment; no monies will be paid if the carrier assigned gives to another carrier.
Compensation for this load will be forfeited and agreed will not be paid if this load is moved via rail.
Current CSA scores must be within satisfactory limits.
Compensation for this load may be withheld if shipment is consolidated with other freight given move type TL and/or exclusive use
Food Products All food products will require either seal or padlock. Food products cannot be shipped with hazardous or odorous
products. Seals provided or required by shipper must be noted on the bill of lading prior to departure.
Seals may not be broken without prior written approval from RJW Logistics. Upon delivery, seal must be broken by consignee only
and padlocks must only be unlocked in presence of Consignee. Failure to adhere to instructions will result in cargo claim.
It is the Carrier's sole responsibility to confirm that it may lawfully and safely operate its vehicle and its contents over any road, highway, bridge and/or route and in compliance
with applicable hours of service regulations. Carrier agrees to immediately notify RJW is unable to lawfully lawfully meet the agreed upon shipping schedule due to hours of
service regulations. Carrier shall be solely responsible for any fine, penalties, or citations that may be levied as a result of operating its vehicle equipment and its contents in any
way that may be found to be in violation of any regulation, law or ordinance. If carrier's insurance policy contains a schedule of covered vehicles, carrier will not transport any
cargo on this shipment using a vehicle that is not listed as a scheduled vehicle on carrier's insurance policy. All travel directions given by RJW are for informational purposes only.
This load confirmation is subject to the terms of the BROKER-CARRIER agreement previously executed between our companies and this confirmation will serve as an
addendum to said broker-carrier agreement. RJW agrees to pay the rates and charges shown above and no different tariff rate or schedules of rates apply. This load confirmation
is inclusive of all charges. Unless oral and written objections are made prior to work being initiated and RJW confirms receipt of objections, you have agreed to these terms.
